### 1. Get List
GET http://localhost:3000/api/releases

### 2. Create New
POST http://localhost:3000/api/releases
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "v3.0.0",
    "date": "2026-05-20T09:00:00Z",
    "additionalInfo": "API Created"
}

### 3. Update (Edit) - Replace {{id}} with an actual ID from Step 1
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/releases?id=4
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "steps": ["merge", "tests"],
    "notes": "Updated via REST Client"
}

### 4. Delete - Replace {{id}} with an actual ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/releases?id=4